Sentencas: This paper describes a preparation method and structural and electrochemical properties of a thin bilayer anode-electrolyte structure for a solid oxide fuel cell operating at intermediate temperatures (IT-SOFC).
Titulo: An ion-plasma technique for formation of anode-supported thin electrolyte films for IT-SOFC applications

Sentencas: Thin anode-supported yttria-stabilized zirconia electrolyte films were prepared by reactive magnetron sputtering of a Zr-Y target in an Ar-O-2 atmosphere.
Titulo: An ion-plasma technique for formation of anode-supported thin electrolyte films for IT-SOFC applications

Sentencas: Porous anode surfaces of IT-SOFCs were modified by a pulsed low-energy high-current electron beam prior to film deposition; the influence of this pretreatment on the performance of both the deposited films and a single cell was investigated.
Titulo: An ion-plasma technique for formation of anode-supported thin electrolyte films for IT-SOFC applications

Sentencas: The optimal conditions of the pulsed electron beam pretreatment were obtained.
